# Ownership

Full matrix: `AGENTS.md` § Ownership matrix.

## Quick rules

| If task mentions… | Edit only |
|-------------------|-----------|
| Rules, dice, phases, events | `packages/game-engine/` + `GAME_MECHANICS.md` |
| Card data, types, clamps | `packages/shared/` |
| UI, animation, audio, stores | `apps/web/` |
| Backend API | `apps/api/` (user must request) |

## Never

- Import `apps/web` from `packages/*`
- Add features to `packages/ui/` (legacy)
- Implement rules in `apps/mock-server` expecting web to use them

## Cross-package order

`shared` → `game-engine` → `apps/web`

Stop after each step; run build for touched workspaces.

